value:
The Bank has implemented various measures to ensure a safe and healthy workplace including:
- Access control systems to manage and monitor entry and exit;
- Annual fire safety training and evacuation drills to enhance preparedness;
- Regular issuance of fire safety advisories to raise awareness;
- Strategic placement of fire safety signage across premises;
- E-surveillance and real-time alert monitoring systems;
- Fire and burglar alarm systems equipped with advanced fire and smoke sensors; and
- Provision of fire extinguishers to support immediate firefighting efforts.
